{"tid":1429273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鐳射筆單野唔好比人spin走！！","createTime":"2019-08-07T12:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T02:06:30.000Z","uid":283177,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a7f9e9bd95ff8ebab7ccdeee9c56b88dcc2f267f","tid":1429273,"uid":283177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日見到post有人搵湯博士。但我想講支鐳射筆幾大能量跟本唔係重點。<br />\n<br />\n今日警犬記者會示範鐳射筆嘅危險性。目的就係為左Spin到大家討論浸大學生會會長係咪真係有買高能量雷射筆。<br />\n<br />\n一樣野係咪武器，唔係睇佢殺傷力幾大，而係睇用嗰個人點用。警犬最大問題係佢覺得你買一般野都可以懷疑你買武器。咁政府不如起liscense唔比人買摺凳，刀，不如禁埋火機，遮，行山用品，飯煲一樣可以做武器，然後叫警犬又示範下點樣用日常用品整爛張報紙咪得。<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"45df70eda0d4a5b71a74b52cc0a267c2b9096218","tid":1429273,"uid":228955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:56:31.000Z","msg":"鐵通可以係水喉可以係殺傷力武器咁點解啲白衫唔拉晒佢"},{"pid":"300e0bcf71e503713c1a5657cba698fa7fa93810","tid":1429273,"uid":707,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:57:37.000Z","msg":"如果咁著火係危險 火機都好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0902a9cd67e1228fcc329be536f4c664816a0405","tid":1429273,"uid":283177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45df70eda0d4a5b71a74b52cc0a267c2b9096218","tid":1429273,"uid":228955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:56:31.000Z","msg":"鐵通可以係水喉可以係殺傷力武器咁點解啲白衫唔拉晒佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"啱呀。所以警犬跟本係狡辯！！！！"},{"pid":"1520f9d06a7415840e19cafd05b4863110dac0cd","tid":1429273,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"唔好比警犬spin到去買鐳射筆=射狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc3d2d0135e7dda780f0de8a8a49460bad37620","tid":1429273,"uid":283177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q